### 2. Tạo đơn hàng với voucher
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/admin/orders/create-with-voucher
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "order": {
        "user_id": 1,
        "event_date": "2025-12-30",
        "guest_count": 100,
        "total_amount": 0,
        "discount_amount": 0,
        "final_amount": 0,
